welcome_message_body: "Welcome to Mwaline al Oued, the charming city known for its vibrant culture and beautiful landscapes. We are excited to have you here and invite you to explore and immerse yourself in all this city has to offer. Enjoy your stay!"

terminals.name: Terminal 1
terminals.description: The main terminal at Mohamed V Airport, serving both domestic and international flights.

terminals.name: Terminal 2
terminals.description: A smaller terminal mainly used for low-cost and charter flights.

terminals.name: Terminal 3
terminals.description: A newly built terminal dedicated to international flights.

wifi.note: Free WiFi is available throughout the airport, but it may be slow and unreliable at times.
